<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Expiring Soon - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffc107;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .status-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ffc107;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .expiry-alert {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        }
        .days-remaining {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e67e22;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .subscription-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .plan-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .expiry-date {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .benefits-lost {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .benefit-item {
            margin: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .benefit-item:before {
            content: "‚ùå";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
        }
        .renewal-section {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .urgency-indicator {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #ffa500);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">{{appName}}</div>
            <div class="status-message">‚è∞ Subscription Expiring Soon!</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <div class="expiry-alert">
                <div class="urgency-indicator">{{#if (lt daysRemaining 3)}}URGENT{{else}}REMINDER{{/if}}</div>
                <p>Your <strong>{{planName}}</strong> subscription is expiring soon!</p>
                <div class="days-remaining">{{daysRemaining}}</div>
                <p><strong>{{#if (eq daysRemaining 1)}}day{{else}}days{{/if}} remaining</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subscription-details">
                <h3>Current Subscription Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Plan:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value plan-name">{{planName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Start Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{startDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Expiry Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value expiry-date">{{expiryDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Alerts Received:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{alertsReceived}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefits-lost">
                <h3>What you'll lose after expiry:</h3>
                {{#each features}}
                <div class="benefit-item">{{this}}</div>
                {{/each}}
                <div class="benefit-item">Access to premium trading alerts</div>
                <div class="benefit-item">Priority customer support</div>
                <div class="benefit-item">Advanced market analytics</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="renewal-section">
                <h3>üöÄ Renew Now & Continue Your Trading Success!</h3>
                <p>Don't miss out on profitable trading opportunities. Renew your subscription today and keep receiving premium alerts.</p>
                
                {{#if renewalUrl}}
                <a href="{{renewalUrl}}" class="cta-button">Renew Subscription Now</a>
                {{else}}
                <p><strong>Contact our support team to renew your subscription:</strong></p>
                <p><a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
                {{/if}}
                
                <p><small>Renewing before expiry ensures uninterrupted service</small></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h3>Need Help?</h3>
                <p>Have questions about renewal or need assistance? Our support team is here to help!</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
                {{#if telegramSupport}}
                <p><strong>Telegram:</strong> {{telegramSupport}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <p>Thank you for being a valued member of {{appName}}. We look forward to continuing to serve you!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>User ID: {{userId}} | Subscription ID: {{subscriptionId}}</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>